verses.text_plain: Praise ye the Lord. Praise ye the Lord from the heavens: praise him in the heights.
verses.verse_html:
1Praise ye the Lord. Praise ye the Lord from the heavens: praise him in the heights. ▼
▼ Praise ye the Lord. Praise: Heb. Hallelujah, etc

footnotes.body_text: ▼ Praise ye the Lord. Praise: Heb. Hallelujah, etc
footnotes.body_html: ▼ Praise ye the Lord. Praise: Heb. Hallelujah, etc

verses.text_plain: Praise ye him, all his angels: praise ye him, all his hosts.
verses.verse_html: 2Praise ye him, all his angels: praise ye him, all his hosts.

verses.text_plain: Praise ye him, sun and moon: praise him, all ye stars of light.
verses.verse_html: 3Praise ye him, sun and moon: praise him, all ye stars of light.

verses.text_plain: Praise him, ye heavens of heavens, and ye waters that be above the heavens.
verses.verse_html: 4Praise him, ye heavens of heavens, and ye waters that be above the heavens.

verses.text_plain: Let them praise the name of the Lord: for he commanded, and they were created.
verses.verse_html: 5Let them praise the name of the Lord: for he commanded, and they were created.

verses.text_plain: He hath also stablished them for ever and ever: he hath made a decree which shall not pass.
verses.verse_html: 6He hath also stablished them for ever and ever: he hath made a decree which shall not pass.

verses.text_plain: Praise the Lord from the earth, ye dragons, and all deeps:
verses.verse_html: 7Praise the Lord from the earth, ye dragons, and all deeps:

verses.text_plain: Fire, and hail; snow, and vapour; stormy wind fulfilling his word:
verses.verse_html: 8Fire, and hail; snow, and vapour; stormy wind fulfilling his word:

verses.text_plain: Mountains, and all hills; fruitful trees, and all cedars:
verses.verse_html: 9Mountains, and all hills; fruitful trees, and all cedars:

verses.text_plain: Beasts, and all cattle; creeping things, and flying fowl:
verses.verse_html:
10Beasts, and all cattle; creeping things, and flying fowl: ▼
▼ flying…: Heb. birds of wing

footnotes.body_html: ▼ flying…: Heb. birds of wing

verses.text_plain: Kings of the earth, and all people; princes, and all judges of the earth:
verses.verse_html: 11Kings of the earth, and all people; princes, and all judges of the earth:

verses.text_plain: Both young men, and maidens; old men, and children:
verses.verse_html: 12Both young men, and maidens; old men, and children:

verses.text_plain: Let them praise the name of the Lord: for his name alone is excellent; his glory is above the earth and heaven.
verses.verse_html:
13Let them praise the name of the Lord: for his name alone is excellent; his glory is above the earth and heaven. ▼
▼ excellent: Heb. exalted

verses.text_plain: He also exalteth the horn of his people, the praise of all his saints; even of the children of Israel, a people near unto him. Praise ye the Lord.
verses.verse_html: 14He also exalteth the horn of his people, the praise of all his saints; even of the children of Israel, a people near unto him. Praise ye the Lord.
